### 测试GitHub GraphQL API权限

@token = YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN_HERE

### 测试基本用户信息
POST https://api.github.com/graphql
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { viewer { login } }"
}

### 测试项目权限
POST https://api.github.com/graphql
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { viewer { login projectsV2(first: 1) { totalCount } } }"
}

### 测试获取项目列表
POST https://api.github.com/graphql
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { viewer { login projectsV2(first: 10) { totalCount nodes { id title } } } }"
}
